      "sessionTarget": "isolated",
      "wakeMode": "now",
      "payload": {
        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "Monitor Shadow's free model providers for changes. This is CRITICAL - alert immediately if any tracked model is deprecated or becomes paid.\n\n## Tracked Models (MUST MONITOR)\n\n**Primary model:** kilocode/z-ai/glm-5:free\n\n**Fallbacks (in order):**\n1. opencode-zen/glm-5-free\n2. nvidia/meta/llama-3.3-70b-instruct\n3. opencode-zen/minimax-m2.5-free\n4. kilocode/minimax/minimax-m2.5:free\n5. opencode-zen/kimi-k2.5-free\n\n## Check Steps\n\n### 1. Check OpenRouter for free model changes\n```\ncurl -s \"https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/models\" | jq '[.data[] | select(.pricing.prompt == \"0\" and .pricing.completion == \"0\") | {id, name, context_length}]'\n```\n\n### 2. Load state file\nRead: ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/free-models-state.json\n\n### 3. Detect CHANGES\n\n**DEPRECATED/REMOVED** - Send URGENT alert if:\n- Any tracked model (primary or fallback) disappears from provider\n- Model was free, now has pricing > 0\n- Model returns 404 or \"not found\"\n\n**NEW POWERFUL FREE MODELS** - Alert if found:\n- Context window >= 64k OR reasoning capability\n- Not already in tracked list\n- From OpenCode, Kilocode, NVIDIA, or major providers\n\n### 4. Alert Format\n\nFor DEPRECATED:\n```\n🚨 MODEL DEPRECATED: <model-id>\nProvider: <provider>\nStatus: No longer available / Now paid ($X/input)\nACTION: Update fallbacks or switch primary model!\n```\n\nFor NEW:\n```\n🆕 NEW POWERFUL FREE MODEL: <model-id>\nProvider: <provider>\nContext: <X>k tokens\nReasoning: yes/no\nRecommendation: Consider adding to fallbacks\n```\n\n### 5. Update state file\nSave new knownFreeModels list to free-models-state.json\n\nOnly send Telegram notification to 55163462 if there are actual changes. Otherwise stay silent.",
        "model": "opencode-zen/glm-5-free",
        "timeoutSeconds": 600
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "none",
        "channel": "telegram",
        "to": "YOUR_CHAT_ID"
      },
